{"tid":766874,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"赫特將以400萬鎊投般尼","createTime":"2018-08-04T03:58:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-04T05:30:32.000Z","uid":31314,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"f3860c482e2805b3f3c3a8254d1f5f0d23da5338","tid":766874,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T03:58:02.000Z","msg":"自領隊哥迪奧拿接掌後已不受重用的赫特，近兩季先後外借拖連奴及韋斯咸，但表現都未算突出，並落選今夏世盃英格蘭大軍名單。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>一直想以1,500萬鎊價錢把赫特賣走的曼城</strong></span>，由於與對方只餘下一年合約，惟有<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>割價至400萬鎊把他放走</strong></span>。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n而般尼因為兩大門將尼克普比及湯希頓同樣受傷，正面對門將荒，球會更已向UEFA申請在下周四對鴨巴甸的歐霸盃外圍賽前，可註冊新龍門在比賽上陣，因此急急收購赫特。"},{"pid":"a46e1b38d8fbc7e15670a186058ac146292e72d8","tid":766874,"uid":2033,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T04:00:15.000Z","msg":"牙joe<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"657ab6d70d2962b672f3d298bf1b7490b1d77293","tid":766874,"uid":165817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T04:08:49.000Z","msg":"Pope fit過佢好多，復出之後阿Joe會唔會又要走人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8113956ec617dd5426471953052dca3a76679aa","tid":766874,"uid":69213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T04:11:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fac458bf5adb9d2ca4fcb6b501ff13eb19daa793","tid":766874,"uid":68916,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T04:11:31.000Z","msg":"on9樓主貼old news<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a519cca9d060c17343b786bd95b841d0295072bc","tid":766874,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T04:11:44.000Z","msg":"快撚d走啦垃圾"},{"pid":"1af9483655cb5a1451661654fe4fda9e417200